snippet.title: Emo Quest XD - Game Trailer
snippet.description:
This is my turn based RPG I've developed in the last 4 years. It's available on Itchio!

A Quest about Soul, Love and Emotion, inspired by retro RPG style!

You're a boy with dark powers, who is playing games, and finds out there are monsters outside! So you decide to go out and defeat them to level up! 

Never lose faith in yourself!

I've started back in 2019, it was a long journey!
